title: HOUR 2- Steve Palazzolo Oct 01, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 2- Steve Palazzolo Oct 01, 2020
description:
Steve Palazzolo gives Dan the grades on some of the quarterbacks from around the NFL. Steve says Sam Darnold is not good but he says the situation is bad around Darnold and he has not progressed for him to be in year 3.
